  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the bulgur in cold water and soak it in water for 30 minutes.",
    "Drain and squeeze out excess water from the bulgur.",
    "Chop the parsley, mint, and scallions finely and mix in a bowl.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes, lemon juice, olive oil, salt, and black pepper to the bowl and mix well.",
    "Fluff the soaked bulgur with a fork and add it to the bowl.",
    "Mix all the ingredients together until they are well combined.",
    "Stir in the rendered plant-based lardons.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Cover and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Serve the tabbouleh chilled, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
